---
import Navbar from '../../components/Navbar.jsx'
import '../../styles/global.css'
import '../../styles/events.css'
---

<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>JCHS FBLA</title>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="header-container">
        <Navbar type="flat" client:load />
    </div>
    <div>
        <div class="event-title">
            NATIONAL LEADERSHIP CONFERENCE (NLC)
        </div>
        <div class="divider-row">
            <hr class="title-divider"/>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="find-event-container">
        <div class="find-event-container-title">Having Trouble Deciding Which Competitive Event To Do?â€‹</div>
        <a href="https://storage.googleapis.com/articulate-courses/BAA%20Contributor/Choose%20Your%20Event%20(FBLA)%20-%20Storyline%20output/story.html" class="find-event-container-link" target="_blank">Click Here for Help Choosing Your Competitive Event</a>
    </div>

    <div class="info-box-container">
        <a href="/nlc/" class="info-box">
            Registration Will Begin After SLC
        </a>
    </div>
    

    <div class="info-container">
        <h1 class="info-title">About NLC</h1>
        <p class="info-description">
            At the National Leadership Conference, members can compete in many events, attend general sessions and keynotes, watch the national officer campaigns, and see national recognitions and competitive event winners. Members who placed in the top 4 for their event at the SLC qualify for the NLC. If members qualify for nationals in multiply events, they can only choose one event to compete in at nationals. 
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="info-container">
        <h1 class="info-title">Pricing & Dates</h1>
        <div class="info-list">
            <div class="info-list-item">
                Dates: June 29 - July 2, 2024
            </div>
            <div class="info-list-item">
                Pricing: $795

            </div>
           
            
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="info-container">
        <h1 class="info-title">Location</h1>
        <div class="info-list">
            <div class="info-list-item">
                Orange County Convention Center & Universal Studios Orlando
            </div>
            <div class="info-list-item">
                9800 International Dr, Orlando, FL 32819
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
